==Arts and entertainment==
===Fictional characters===
*Spencer, character in &quot;Beyblade&quot;
*Spencer, character from &quot;Final Fantasy Mystic Quest&quot;
*Spencer family (&quot;General Hospital&quot;), on &quot;General Hospital&quot;
