* Metro Nightclub, the former name of the Palace theatre, Melbourne, Australia

===Periodicals===
====Magazines====
* &quot;Metro&quot; (magazine), New Zealand lifestyle magazine
* &quot;Metro Magazine&quot;, for bus and rail transit and motorcoach operators
